WEBVTT

00:19.436 --> 00:20.937
The real fight starts now.

00:38.997 --> 00:40.206
Such... a shame.

00:51.718 --> 00:53.303
Let's pull back for now!

00:53.386 --> 00:56.056
That’s... enough.

01:04.564 --> 01:08.693
I don't intend to die.
My goal is to return alive.

01:11.362 --> 01:12.238
To live...

01:13.323 --> 01:14.908
and see my wife.

01:25.210 --> 01:28.254
- Sagiri?
- Nothing. Let's hurry.

01:29.756 --> 01:33.092
We need to reach the source
of the elixir as soon as possible.

01:33.885 --> 01:35.762
That’s our duty right now.

01:36.513 --> 01:38.431
We don’t have time to stand around.

01:43.770 --> 01:46.397
Yes, I'm sure Gabimaru can handle himself.

01:48.608 --> 01:50.902
And the others too.

03:25.246 --> 03:30.668
‎A FEW MOMENTS EARLIER -
‎BED CHAMBER ARTS PALACE

03:43.473 --> 03:44.766
Come here, Toma.

03:46.059 --> 03:48.228
I've already come
to an understanding with them.

03:48.853 --> 03:51.147
If you join us, you’ll gain immortality.

03:51.231 --> 03:54.150
It's adaptation. Come up here.

03:55.026 --> 03:57.403
Brother. Why are you here?

03:58.112 --> 04:01.574
No, it doesn't matter. More importantly...

04:04.077 --> 04:08.206
Go on. That’s your beloved
big brother, right? Get moving.

04:08.915 --> 04:11.042
What, are you holding back because of us?

04:11.626 --> 04:14.796
Are you sure about this?
Worst case, it’ll be four against two.

04:17.131 --> 04:20.802
Even if some small fry joins in,
it won’t hurt in the slightest.

04:21.511 --> 04:24.055
I’ll cut all of you down together.

04:24.639 --> 04:27.308
So he says. Well then, bye-bye.

04:37.819 --> 04:41.906
Such an obvious insult.
Was that to make him snap?

04:42.991 --> 04:45.576
You’re more soft-hearted than I expected.

04:45.660 --> 04:47.495
Don’t get the wrong idea.

04:48.121 --> 04:52.333
A wavering enemy is easier to control
than a wavering ally, that’s all.

04:53.418 --> 04:55.962
Hmm... I see. That works too.

05:56.856 --> 05:58.983
Looks like you haven’t gone soft, Toma.

06:01.152 --> 06:02.528
Are you making fun of me?

06:05.573 --> 06:07.742
"Undo the braids if it’s a lie."

06:08.826 --> 06:10.536
That’s a basic signal, right?

06:15.583 --> 06:17.752
No, I’m talking about your movement.

06:18.503 --> 06:20.046
You’re better now.

06:20.838 --> 06:25.301
You’ve gotten even more handsome.
I barely recognized you.

06:30.181 --> 06:32.934
You guys too, thanks for looking
after my little brother!

06:33.017 --> 06:35.353
For that much, I’ll give you my thanks!

06:35.436 --> 06:37.105
Thank you for everything.

06:37.188 --> 06:41.109
As thanks, I’ll give you this one.
Take it. No need to refuse it.

06:41.192 --> 06:43.528
That was more poor character
than becoming our enemy.

06:43.611 --> 06:44.612
Agreed.

06:45.279 --> 06:46.489
So mean!

06:46.572 --> 06:47.615
Huh?!

06:47.698 --> 06:50.993
I thought we could be friends, too!

06:51.619 --> 06:53.996
Want me to comfort you?

06:54.872 --> 06:57.875
What? Totally not my type.

06:59.335 --> 07:02.088
Betrayal. An ambush.

07:02.171 --> 07:05.383
Humans really are sly
and shitty to the core.

07:05.967 --> 07:08.469
You hurt Tao Fa.

07:08.553 --> 07:10.638
Don’t think you’ll get away with this.

07:10.721 --> 07:12.223
Shitty?

07:12.932 --> 07:15.643
Immortals sure talk elegantly, don't they?

07:15.726 --> 07:18.146
We’re bandits!

07:20.606 --> 07:23.651
We deceive, scheme, and steal everything!

07:23.734 --> 07:26.320
We’re the infamous Aza brothers of Iyo!

07:36.497 --> 07:38.040
It’s just like last time.

07:49.135 --> 07:51.637
No matter how many times,
it’s always the same!

08:18.456 --> 08:20.791
Senjutsu: Suzusashi.

08:28.090 --> 08:29.675
That was close.

08:30.426 --> 08:31.260
Sorry.

08:31.802 --> 08:33.679
But good movement.

08:34.597 --> 08:35.431
‎Thank you!

08:35.515 --> 08:38.768
His scar shows when he gets fired up?

08:38.851 --> 08:39.936
He's easy to read.

08:57.245 --> 08:58.955
These two, it’s like...

09:03.417 --> 09:05.586
Two people acting as one.

09:12.843 --> 09:16.764
This man...
He can perceive Tao and wield it.

09:17.598 --> 09:19.517
His physical ability has increased too.

09:21.102 --> 09:24.272
But the biggest change is him.

09:25.898 --> 09:30.278
To hell with finesse.
What you need for a sword is guts.

09:34.240 --> 09:37.535
The resolve to kill with your own hands,
that’s what matters.

09:43.165 --> 09:45.418
It’s the complete opposite
of back then, huh?

09:47.878 --> 09:50.798
Two as one... No...

09:51.591 --> 09:53.801
One acting as two!

09:55.720 --> 09:56.804
Makes me sick.

09:57.972 --> 10:00.057
I don’t care about the ritual.

10:00.141 --> 10:02.393
I’ll kill you again!

10:10.151 --> 10:12.862
I’m super bummed
about getting my head cut off,

10:12.945 --> 10:15.448
but Rien gets scary
if I don’t follow orders.

10:17.908 --> 10:20.328
So let’s wrap this up quick!

10:21.162 --> 10:22.705
Yo-yo!

10:22.788 --> 10:24.707
Absolutely top-tier!

10:24.790 --> 10:29.962
Great ass! Great chest!
A picture-perfect woman!

10:30.046 --> 10:31.964
- Agreed.
- Huh?!

10:32.548 --> 10:36.510
Regeneration ability, an inhuman physique.

10:36.594 --> 10:38.596
You’re exactly like a fairy-tale immortal.

10:38.679 --> 10:42.058
Wow! Thanks!

10:42.141 --> 10:43.184
She's fast!

10:52.943 --> 10:56.238
But being praised by some old guy
actually gives me goosebumps.

10:57.823 --> 11:00.493
Oh? You’re cuter than I expected.

11:02.578 --> 11:04.622
Want to do bedchamber arts with me?

11:04.705 --> 11:06.666
I’ll turn you into Tan anyway.

11:09.043 --> 11:11.253
I hate to brush you off,

11:12.129 --> 11:15.007
but I’m only interested
in what’s inside of you.

11:15.091 --> 11:17.259
Huh? Inside of me?

11:17.343 --> 11:20.763
Pervert! If you wanna see, I’ll show you.

11:20.846 --> 11:22.556
- So cold.
- Oh?

11:25.226 --> 11:29.647
Sexy, strong, killing you
would make my name famous.

11:29.730 --> 11:32.775
You’re my ideal woman.

11:33.442 --> 11:35.277
Play with me a little longer.

11:37.488 --> 11:40.032
Well then, here I go!

12:07.435 --> 12:08.519
Well done!

12:20.406 --> 12:24.034
So close! But you’re both strong!

12:25.286 --> 12:28.038
That’s the so-called
"invisible attack" Tao!

12:28.831 --> 12:31.125
One more time, whatever-your-name-is-Mon!

12:33.377 --> 12:34.753
It's Asaemon.

12:35.421 --> 12:37.673
We can’t win like this.

12:39.008 --> 12:40.885
To defeat a Tensen,

12:40.968 --> 12:44.180
we have to destroy
the Tanden with opposing Tao.

12:44.263 --> 12:47.850
But unlike Gabimaru
and Shio and the others,

12:47.933 --> 12:51.937
you and I still can’t use Tao properly.

13:06.577 --> 13:11.457
Now then! It's been a while
since the Rite of... Abstaining...

13:11.540 --> 13:15.461
Rite of Abstaining and Sustaining Life!
Right? I said it!

13:16.337 --> 13:17.963
So, who are today’s offerings?

13:18.589 --> 13:21.258
A super-strong old guy

13:21.342 --> 13:23.594
and a super-quick little guy.

13:26.180 --> 13:27.515
Just as I thought.

13:30.100 --> 13:33.145
Tao is not something
you can see with your eyes.

13:33.729 --> 13:36.232
That’s why, to fight using Tao,

13:36.315 --> 13:39.735
you must first begin by feeling Tao.

13:40.444 --> 13:41.278
Now then...

13:45.199 --> 13:48.285
Well? Can you feel my Tao?

13:48.369 --> 13:49.703
No.

13:57.753 --> 14:02.299
Not only can we not see Tao-based attacks,
but defense seems useless too.

14:03.926 --> 14:05.177
That Tensen...

14:05.261 --> 14:08.889
Her name is indeed Tao Fa,
attribute "wood".

14:08.973 --> 14:13.060
I’m "metal", which would be overcoming,
so normally we’d have the advantage, but

14:13.602 --> 14:16.939
since we can’t use Tao,
the effect will be weak.

14:17.022 --> 14:18.774
We need to come up with something.

14:18.857 --> 14:19.817
Shut up!

14:19.900 --> 14:23.404
Don’t ever use that word
"Tao" in front of me again.

14:23.487 --> 14:25.823
It’s too damn complicated to remember!

14:26.907 --> 14:30.327
Things were just getting fun.
Don’t ruin the mood!

14:31.287 --> 14:32.371
Fun?

14:37.334 --> 14:39.086
Tao is important.

14:39.169 --> 14:41.213
You can read
your opponent’s movements too.

14:42.423 --> 14:45.968
I see, you’re on a different level
from those Doshi.

14:55.436 --> 14:57.271
You can control direction
however you want!

15:01.775 --> 15:04.028
See? Handy, right?

15:05.779 --> 15:09.909
Why don’t you give up already?
You can’t win without Tao.

15:09.992 --> 15:13.037
I'd be pleased if you'd just
let me turn you into Tan.

15:14.246 --> 15:18.542
You’re enjoying this too, aren’t you?

15:18.626 --> 15:22.046
You’ve been tormenting humans
for a thousand years, after all.

15:28.260 --> 15:31.180
I’m not enjoying this at all. Not one bit.

15:32.389 --> 15:34.683
Staying here,
training for immortality forever,

15:35.976 --> 15:38.938
luring humans in to use as nourishment,

15:39.647 --> 15:41.190
over and over,

15:41.899 --> 15:43.692
for a thousand years.

15:44.652 --> 15:46.737
But I'm sure that even if
we do it another thousand,

15:47.529 --> 15:50.950
we’ll never reach perfect immortality.

15:53.577 --> 15:55.871
Mu Dan realized it.

15:55.955 --> 15:59.166
Ju Fa too. Deep down, everyone knows.

16:00.292 --> 16:03.337
If I don't laugh, I'll go crazy!

16:04.964 --> 16:08.467
Or maybe I can laugh
because I've already gone crazy?

16:13.681 --> 16:16.350
I’m not enjoying this at all.

16:23.899 --> 16:26.819
Tao... I didn’t realize
it was this powerful.

16:28.737 --> 16:30.072
Have you given up?

16:30.155 --> 16:33.492
I think it’s better to die
an easy death than to suffer.

16:35.869 --> 16:38.288
This is an incredible discovery.

16:38.372 --> 16:41.000
A whole new frontier in life science!

16:41.083 --> 16:43.460
More than anything,
being able to touch it is wonderful!

16:43.544 --> 16:46.088
It’s like gaining a whole new organ!

16:47.089 --> 16:51.510
If I bring this knowledge back, it'll turn
the world of medicine upside down!

16:52.094 --> 16:54.304
I thought I'd studied plenty,

16:54.388 --> 16:57.016
but there are still so many new fields.

16:57.766 --> 17:00.519
I told you, didn't I? Don't ruin the mood.

17:01.520 --> 17:05.774
Playing with a new toy
is the most fun there is.

17:06.358 --> 17:08.193
It does feel like
we’re the ones being played with.

17:08.277 --> 17:09.278
Shut up!

17:10.904 --> 17:13.782
You really do look like you're having fun.

17:16.118 --> 17:17.578
Must be nice...

17:20.998 --> 17:23.542
You guys are messed up in here.

17:24.126 --> 17:25.419
- So are you!
- So are you!

17:25.502 --> 17:28.213
There's no art
in just charging straight in!

17:32.259 --> 17:34.553
What is this?

17:36.138 --> 17:37.431
This feeling?

17:50.027 --> 17:51.945
He dodged the Tao!

17:52.029 --> 17:53.614
I see.

17:53.697 --> 17:56.325
I figured everything out about Tao!

17:59.536 --> 18:02.456
You can’t see anything at all.
Was that just a fluke?

18:06.585 --> 18:09.463
I think Nurugai’s age has something
to do with it as well, but...

18:10.089 --> 18:12.299
the reason you three
can’t handle Tao well is...

18:12.382 --> 18:13.383
It's...

18:13.467 --> 18:15.094
Well, how should I put it?

18:16.011 --> 18:17.513
You're all too thickheaded.

18:18.430 --> 18:22.351
All three of you don’t believe
in things you can’t see, right?

18:23.185 --> 18:25.229
You can’t wield Tao with your head.

18:25.854 --> 18:29.608
You have to shut out reality
and entrust yourself to your senses.

18:30.275 --> 18:32.694
Try a little harder, you two!

18:32.778 --> 18:33.904
Not interested.

18:33.987 --> 18:36.448
I don’t waste time on things I can’t do.

18:36.532 --> 18:39.284
I only believe in what I can cut.

18:39.368 --> 18:41.745
I can’t accept what I can’t touch.

18:42.329 --> 18:45.582
Until I open it up, extract it,
and touch it myself...

18:45.666 --> 18:47.126
What are you even talking about?

18:47.209 --> 18:50.045
We’re not really comrades or anything.

18:50.129 --> 18:52.881
Everyone can do whatever they want.

18:57.136 --> 18:58.011
Bye-bye.

19:07.062 --> 19:09.940
I see, Little-mon. That I understand!

19:10.023 --> 19:14.069
That’s just a stopgap!
More importantly, observe carefully!

19:14.153 --> 19:15.988
If you can feel Tao...

19:17.406 --> 19:19.908
it’ll become a chance... to counterattack!

19:26.623 --> 19:29.084
At point-blank range,
isn’t it impossible to dodge?

19:47.394 --> 19:50.063
So you’re just going to keep
taking the hits like that?

19:50.147 --> 19:52.816
Just to let him observe Tao?

19:53.775 --> 19:56.320
How caring of your comrade, how lovely!

19:56.945 --> 20:00.073
We're not... comrades!

20:01.325 --> 20:03.577
We may not be "comrades," but...

20:03.660 --> 20:06.455
I think we're something similar.

20:07.206 --> 20:10.209
You’re an executioner, right?
You sure that’s okay?

20:10.292 --> 20:14.213
You’re pretty caring yourself,
with Toma and all.

20:15.422 --> 20:17.216
I understand my position.

20:17.299 --> 20:20.594
And if there are crimes,
I don’t intend to justify them.

20:22.596 --> 20:25.098
But I touched it.

20:26.683 --> 20:28.101
Executioners are human too.

20:29.186 --> 20:31.605
Get deeply involved, and feelings arise.

20:33.190 --> 20:37.611
In this short yet intense time,
I opened my heart,

20:37.694 --> 20:40.572
extracted, and touched.

20:41.448 --> 20:43.784
Once I touched it, it was nothing special.

20:43.867 --> 20:45.869
Samurai and criminals are the same.

20:46.620 --> 20:48.622
Blood, flesh, bone...

20:48.705 --> 20:51.375
and the single wish to live, that's all.

20:51.458 --> 20:53.335
Just like dissection.

20:55.754 --> 20:58.340
That comparison’s too dangerous.
I’m not following.

21:00.550 --> 21:01.969
Then I won’t say it again.

21:02.052 --> 21:02.886
Huh?!

21:04.972 --> 21:08.392
That I truly wish for everyone to survive,

21:08.475 --> 21:11.144
I’ll never say it again.

21:15.941 --> 21:18.902
If you're not comrades,
then no one has to be sad!

21:23.240 --> 21:25.409
I can’t see anything, but...

21:26.243 --> 21:28.912
I can tell by instinct,
the little guy's in trouble!

21:29.496 --> 21:32.916
You have to shut out reality
and entrust yourself to your senses.

21:46.763 --> 21:49.850
The reason I was able to perceive
Tao that one time was...

21:50.767 --> 21:53.437
because blood blurred one of my eyes.

21:55.022 --> 21:58.317
Because I couldn’t see,
I relied on my senses.

22:01.778 --> 22:05.365
One eye gouged out, the other blurred...

22:06.074 --> 22:08.744
I see, now I can’t see anything.

22:10.078 --> 22:13.749
But this time, I can feel it clearly!

22:24.426 --> 22:25.927
He dodged again.

22:26.011 --> 22:27.596
Amazing, Gantetsu.

22:35.020 --> 22:38.940
You really are the best woman.
I thank you!

22:42.152 --> 22:44.488
Each time it’s heated and hammered,

22:44.571 --> 22:47.824
it grows sharper, harder, stronger!

22:47.908 --> 22:49.076
Penis.

22:49.159 --> 22:50.327
The sword?

22:51.870 --> 22:54.831
This is getting interesting!

24:22.210 --> 24:25.922
Subtitle translation by: Maslin Friedman
